{"tid":1753842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地打撚完飛機未 同你地繼續咁既態度 立法會輸鳩硬","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T17:42:07.000Z","uid":252492,"like":75,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1b743db34da9164dbc49eadd83c423998cc23683","tid":1753842,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"根本咁多年選舉泛民肯協調就有今日成果<br />\n但屆屆都係鬼打鬼 民主黨好似今次帝怡咁夾硬派人空降想趕自己友走攪到欖炒<br />\n<br />\n成班人係到打哂飛機 想立法會輸到仆街？<br />\n<br />\n預見到既有：<br />\n1)  法庭唔比記者查住戶 黎緊立法會政府一定做野瘋狂種票<br />\n今次好多區都係相差超小票數<br />\n<br />\n2)  民主黨變返泛民第一大黨 林卓廷果班人下次立會一定好似帝怡咁唔協調照派人空降撞區<br />\n<br />\n3)  泛民過往經驗好多人當選後地區工作都做唔好 之後立會同下屆區選都比當地居民踢走變建制地盤<br />\n<br />\n繼續好似你班友咁 完全唔諗埋可能發展係出面打哂飛機圍爐 下次立會輸鳩硬"},{"pid":"4c8d514e7663b04a3c6c96ba28bf7696b6aee8fc","tid":1753842,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5704d56113c9a092f536d8da16186d3191e0a7","tid":1753842,"uid":216664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"登記做功能組別選民<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FC.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2FFC.htm&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM294L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d686dacf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FC.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftVLYZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftVLYZQ.png&h=12948fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71475278b90a2e21a1d4d8319e0f6d3db6ce9fe4","tid":1753842,"uid":83913,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你邊位啊<br />\n<br />\n輪到你出聲咩<br />\n<br />\n大肆慶祝先係同人宣揚我哋贏咗<br />\n<br />\n贏民心，<br />\n<br />\n等啲勝利球迷知道企邊面<br />\n<br />\n你條仆街扮野就死撚埋一面啦"},{"pid":"803b041e8034997ef17cd650fc67f523e05521cb","tid":1753842,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":8,"scor